years%20in%20power%20in%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20maintained%20close%20ties%20with%20Chinese%20leaders%20and%20furthered%20the%20strategic%20ties%20with%20Beijing%20viewed%20widely%20as%20a%20strategic%20alliance%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20had%20an%20uneasy%20relationship%20with%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20government%20which%20was%20blamed%20for%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20USD%2060%20billion%20CPEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20providing%20forex%20loans%20and%20rollover%20of%20its%20debt%20periodically%20to%20bail%20out%20Pakistan%20which%20is%20facing%20a%20severe%20economic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20from%20Islamabad%20said%20China%20has%20agreed%20to%20roll%20over%20a%20USD%20two%20billion%20loan%20due%20to%20be%20paid%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710051120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fg89ud168_asif-ali-zardari-xi-jinping_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-wish-to-new-pakistan-president-asif-ali-zardari-xi-jinping-cites-iron-clad-friendship-5210671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20Sunday%20congratulated%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20on%20his%20election%20as%20the%20Pakistan%20President%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Biron-clad%20friendship%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bchoice%20of%20history%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-wish-to-new-pakistan-president-asif-ali-zardari-xi-jinping-cites-iron-clad-friendship-5210671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shaitaan%20scores%20less%20than%2