onducted%20fairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BElection%20Commission%20or%20Election%20OMISSION%3F%20India%20now%20has%20only%20one%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20even%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20to%20be%20announced%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20Why%3F%20As%20I%20have%20said%20earlier%2C%20if%20we%20do%20not%20stop%20the%20systematic%20decimation%20of%20our%20independent%20institutions%2C%20our%20democracy%20shall%20be%20usurped%20by%20dictatorship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20will%20now%20be%20among%20the%20last%20Constitutional%20institutions%20to%20fall%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20new%20process%20of%20selecting%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%20has%20now%20effectively%20given%20all%20the%20power%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20PM%2C%20why%20has%20the%20new%20Election%20Commissioner%20not%20appointed%20even%20after%2023%20days%20of%20the%20completion%20of%20latter's%20tenure%3F%20Modi%20government%20must%20answer%20these%20questions%20and%20come%20out%20with%20a%20reasonable%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20or%20Election%20OMISSION%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20now%20has%20only%20ONE%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20even%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20to%20be%20announced%20in%20few%20days.%20Why%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20I%20have%20said%20earlier%2C%20if%20we%20do%20NOT%20stop%20the%20systematic%20decimation%20of%20our%20independent%20institutions%2C%20our%20DEMOCRACY%20shall%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1766514087188435427%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Goel%20resigned%20on%20Saturday%2C%20days%20before%20the%20expected%20announcement%20of%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20His%20tenure%20was%20till%20December%205%2C%202027%2C%20and%20he%20would%20have%20become%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20after%20incumbent%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20retired%20in%20February%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20consisting%20of%20three%20members%2C%20already%20had%20a%20vacant%20position%2C%20and%20now%2C%20only%20Mr%20Kumar%20remains%20on%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20dates%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20next%20week.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Goel's%20unexpected%20departure%20has%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20previously%20anticipated%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%20also%20criticised%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20constitutional%20institutions%20like%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20highlighted%20the%20alleged%20pressures%20exerted%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20quite%20shocking%3B%20just%20before%20the%20declaration%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20Election%20Commissioner%20has%20resigned.%20Now%2C%20only%20one%20Election%20Commissioner%20is%20there...%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20this%20Election%20Commission%3F%20The%20entire%20country%20is%20anxious.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20doesn't%20want%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20drew%20parallels%20with%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20citing%20the%20case%20of%20Ashok%20Lavasa%2C%20who%20dissented%20against%20giving%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20He%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20remain%20completely%20non-partisan%20to%20preserve%20democratic%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Ashok%20Lavasa%20had%20dissented%20against%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20PM%20for%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20Later%2C%20he%20faced%20relentless%20inquiries.%20This%20attitude%20shows%20the%20regime%20is%20hell-bent%20on%20destroying%20democratic%20traditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Venugopal%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710047880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1f219hp_arun-goel_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farun-goel-resignation-live-updates-reactions-congress-sounds-alarm-bells-as-election-commissioner-arun-goel-abruptly-resigns-5210373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Election%20Commissioner%20Arun%20Goel's%20resignation%20just%20days%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20dates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20within%20the%20political%20circles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farun-goel-resignation-live-updates-reactions-congress-sounds-alarm-bells-as-election-commissioner-arun-goel-abruptly-resigns-5210373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farun-goel-resignation-live-updates-reactions-congress-sounds-alarm-bells-as-election-commissioner-arun-goel-abruptly-resigns-5210373%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farun-goel-resignation-live-updates-reactions-congress-sounds-alarm-bells-as-election-commissioner-arun-goel-abruptly-resigns-5210373%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia's%20stylish%20top%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%202.4%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710047766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108362642%2Cimgsize-25988.cms%22%2C%22originID%