%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1766554149137563830%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20India's%20call%20for%20greater%20representation%2C%20the%20G4%20countries%E2%80%94India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Japan%E2%80%94emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20reflecting%20the%20diversity%20and%20plurality%20of%20views%20from%20the%20193%20member%20states%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20non-permanent%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20practical%20move%2C%20Kamboj%20suggested%20identifying%20specific%20groups%20or%20countries%20deserving%20special%20consideration%20in%20the%20reform%20process%20and%20listening%20carefully%20to%20their%20voices.%20%26quot%3BMember%20states%20should%20also%20make%20full%20use%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20cross-regional%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%20membership%20is%20adequately%20reflected%20in%20the%20Council%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20move%20the%20discussion%20from%20the%20abstract%20to%20the%20concrete%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20for%20member%20states%20to%20first%20identify%20and%20define%20which%20specific%20groups%20or%20countries%20deserve%20special%20consideration%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20then%20carefully%20listen%20to%20their%20voices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20February%2017%2C%20Ms%20Kamboj%20had%20reiterated%20India's%20support%20for%20comprehensive%20reforms%20of%20the%20UNSC%20across%20all%20five%20clusters%2C%20including%20an%20expansion%20in%20both%20the%20permanent%20and%20non-permanent%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710047700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fh8kut7og_ruchira-kamboj_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frisk-oblivion-if-indias-stark-warning-to