%20poached%20these%20AAP%20councillors%20before%20the%20SC%20order%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20case%20of%20a%20fresh%20mayoral%20election%2C%20it%20could%20come%20up%20the%20winner.%C2%A0But%20the%20apex%20court%20reinstated%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20candidate%2C%20catching%20the%20BJP%20by%20surprise%20and%20also%20leaving%20it%20humiliated%20since%20the%20guilty%20presiding%20officer%20was%20a%20BJP%20appointee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20did%20get%20some%20poll%20advantage%20from%20the%20AAP%20defectors%20as%20it%20won%20re-election%20on%20the%20post%20of%20senior%20deputy%20mayor%20and%20deputy%20mayor%20on%20March%204.%20But%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20a%20commanding%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20now%20favours%20the%20INDIA%20block%20as%20two%20AAP%20councillors%20%E2%80%93%20Poonam%20and%20Neha%20%E2%80%93%20took%20AAP%20membership%20again%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouncillor%20Neha%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20by%20AAP%20with%20the%20media%20that%20while%20living%20together%2C%20discords%20occur.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20here%20between%20the%20party%20and%20her.%20But%20now%20she%20has%20decided%20to%20forget%20this%20and%20return%20home.%20Councillor%20Poonam%20said%20that%20now%20she%20has%20no%20problem%20and%20she%20is%20very%20happy%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20fresh%20comments%20on%20Sunday%2C%20their%20return%20has%20nonetheless%20put%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20in%20a%20comfortable%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20numbers%2C%20AAP%20now%20has%2012%20councillors%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%20seven.%20Together%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20have%2019%20councillors%2C%20more%20than%20required%20number%20for%20a%20majority%20in%20the%2035-member%20Chandigarh%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20councillors%20rejoined%20AAP%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bh