20film%20star%20Sophia%20Leone%20has%20died%20at%2026%20after%20being%20found%20%26quot%3Bunresponsive%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20apartment%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20her%20stepfather%20Mike%20Romero%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESophia%20was%20found%20%26quot%3Bunresponsive%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20apartment%20in%20the%20US%20on%20March%201%20by%20her%20family%2C%20Romero%20wrote%20on%20GoFundMe%2C%20as%20he%20sought%20funds%20for%20her%20memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20her%20mother%20and%20family%2C%20it%20is%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20that%20I%20have%20to%20share%20the%20news%20of%20our%20beloved%20Sophia's%20passing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sudden%20loss%20of%20Sophia%20has%20left%20her%20family%20and%20friends%20devastated%20and%20in%20shock.%20On%20top%20of%20the%20difficult%20process%20of%20grieving%20and%20seeking%20justice%20for%20Sophia%2C%20the%20family%20is%20also%20facing%20the%20financial%20burden%20that%20they%20were%20not%20prepared%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Romero%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20an%20investigation%20by%20local%20police%20into%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20still%20currently%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20modeling%20agency%2C%20101%20Modeling%2C%20also%20confirmed%20the%20news%20and%20said%20that%20their%20%26quot%3Bhearts%20are%20broken%20by%20the%20untimely%20and%20tragic%20passing%20of%20our%20beloved%20Sophia%20Leone%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20beautiful%20spirit%20who%20touched%20many%20of%20us.%20RIP%20sweet%20angel%20and%20know%20how%20much%20we%20loved%20you.%20A%20gofund%20me%20has%20been%20started%20for%20her%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20101%20Modeling%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20that%20she%20didn't%20die%20of%20suicide%20and%20that%20her%20death%20was%20being%20investigated%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhome%20invasion%20homicide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3