20based%20on%2020%20FIRs%20registered%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Police%20against%20M%2Fs%20Broadsons%20Commodities%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(BCPL)%20whose%20director%20is%20Subhash%20Yadav.%20The%20FIRs%20accused%20BCPL%20of%20engaging%20in%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20and%20sale%20without%20using%20e-challans%2C%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20about%20environmental%20regulations%20and%20revenue%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMLA%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20a%20staggering%20Rs%20161%20crore%20had%20been%20generated%20through%20the%20illegal%20sale%20of%20sand.%20The%20illicit%20sand%20trade%20is%20reportedly%20controlled%20by%20a%20syndicate%2C%20with%20members%20investing%20funds%20in%20companies%20like%20BCPL%20and%20profiting%20from%20the%20unauthorised%20sale%20of%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20Yadav%20is%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20syndicate%2C%20and%20the%20ED's%20searches%20on%20Saturday%20at%20six%20premises%20in%20Patna%20linked%20to%20him%20and%20his%20close%20associates%20have%20unearthed%20crucial%20evidence.%20Cash%20exceeding%20Rs%202.3%20crore%20and%20incriminating%20documents%20were%20seized%20during%20the%20raids%2C%20leading%20to%20Subhash%20Yadav's%20arrest%20late%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20crackdown%20on%20Subhash%20Yadav%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20similar%20actions%20against%20other%20alleged%20members%20of%20the%20sand%20mining%20syndicate.%20Earlier%20arrests%20included%20JD(U)%20leader%20and%20Bihar%20Legislative%20Council%20member%20Radha%20Charan%20Sah%20and%20his%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20political%20affiliations%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20Subhash%20Yadav%20had%20contested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202019.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20has%20also%20carried%20out%20raids%20at%20Subhash%20Yadav's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710044280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F24o5afc8_su