him%20a%20death%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20video%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20he%20had%20invited%20Mr%20Thakur%20to%20his%20home%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20he%20leaked%20the%20screenshots%20of%20their%20chat%20to%20provoke%20him.%20%26quot%3BMaxtern%20made%20some%20statements%20about%20my%20family%20and%20threatened%20to%20burn%20me%20and%20my%20family%20alive.%20I%20abused%20him%20over%20this%20and%20told%20him%20I%20would%20come%20and%20meet%20him%20wherever%20he%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20finally%20met%20at%20a%20garments%20shop%20owned%20by%20Maxtern's%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20he%20was%20set%20up%20and%20there%20were%20cameras%20hidden%20everywhere.%20He%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20threatened%20to%20kill%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20but%20maintained%20it%20was%20said%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bheat%20of%20the%20moment%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20justified%20his%20action%20saying%20the%20comments%20against%20his%20family%20enraged%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElvish%20Yadav%20is%20not%20new%20to%20controversies.%20He%20is%20already%20in%20legal%20trouble%20over%20the%20snake%20venom-rave%20party%20case.%20He%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20supply%20and%20use%20of%20snake%20venom.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710042600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fa9hpi2c_elvish-yadav_625x300_08_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-called-for-questioning-by-cops-for-assaulting-youtuber-5210262%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gurugram%20Police%20has%20called%20Bigg%20Boss%20OTT%202%20winner%20Elvish%20Yadav%20for%20questioning%20after%20he%20was%20filmed%20assaulting%20a%20YouTuber.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felvish-yadav-called-for-questioning-by-cops-for-assaulting-youtuber-5210262%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Robert%20De%20Niro%20Says%20He%20Would%20Never%20Play%20Trump%3A%20''He%20Is%20A%20Total%20Monster''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHollywood%20icon%20Robert%20De%20Niro%C2%A0has%20said%20he%20would%20never%20portray%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20any%20film%2C%20as%20he%20''cannot%20see%20any%20good''%20in%20him.%20The%2080-year-old%20Hollywood%20actor's%20statement%20came%20during%20his%20recent%20discussion%20on%20the%20upcoming%20US%20presidential%20election%20during%20an%20interview%20on%20HBO's%20'Real%20Time'%2C%20with%20Bill%20Maher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outspoken%20Oscar-winning%20actor%20said%20he%20would%20not%20want%20Trump%20to%20become%20president%20again%20and%20also%20urged%20voters%20to%20vote%20for%20Joe%20Biden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20wanna%20live%20in%20a%20world%20that%20we%20want%20to%20live%20in%20and%20enjoy%20living%20in%2C%20or%20live%20in%20a%20nightmare%3F%20Vote%20for%20Trump%20and%20you'll%20get%20the%20nightmare%2C%20vote%20for%20Biden%20and%20we'll%20be%20back%20to%20normalcy.%C2%A0%C2%A0just%20don't%20want%20to%20feel%20the%20way%20I%20did%2C%20and%20many%20of%20us%20don't%2C%20after%20the%20election%20in%202016%20where%20we%20couldn't%20believe%20that%20it%20happened.%20The%20guy%20is%20a%20total%20monster.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20a%20critic%20of%20the%20former%20President%2C%20further%20insisted%20that%20he%20would%20never%20play%20a%20role%20portraying%20him%20because%20of%20his%20character.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''He's%20such%20a%20mean%2C%20nasty%2C%20hateful%20person.%20I'd%20never%20play%20him%20as%20an%20actor%20because%20I%20can't%20see%20any%20good%20in%20him.%20Nothing.%20Nothing%20at%20all.%20Nothing%20redeemable%20in%20him.%20Whoever%20the%20people%20are%20who%20want%20to%20vote%20for%20him-%20and%20they%20look%20like%20intelligent%20people%20around%20there%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20it%20can't%20be.%20It%20can%20not%20be%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20wins%20the%20election%2C%20you%20won't%20be%20on%20this%20show%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned%20Mr%20Maher.%20%26quot%3BHe'll%20come%20looking%20for%20me.%20There'll%20be%20things%20that%20happen%20that%20none%20of%20us%20can%20imagine.%20That's%20what%20happens%20in%20that%20kind%20of%20dictatorship%2C%20which%20is%20what%20he%20says.%20Let's%20believe%20him%2C%20take%20him%20at%20his%20word.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20sociopathic%2C%20psychopathic%2C%20malignant%20narcissist.%20He%20is%20a%20dangerous%20person%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20help%20people%E2%80%A6%20the%20people%20who%20somehow%20think%20he's%20gonna%20be%20the%20answer%20to%20their%20prayers%2C%20whatever%20those%20are%2C''%20De%20Niro%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20statement%2C%C2%A0the%20former%20president%20called%20De%20Niro%20''a%20stupid-sounding%20guy%2C%20a%20low%20IQ%20individual.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRobert%20DeNiro%20has%20a%20terminal%20case%20of%20Trump%20Derangement%20Syndrome%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20actor%20has%20frequently%20criticised%20Trump%20and%C2%A0they%20often%20sparred%20during%20the%20former%20president's%20time%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710042420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc1ov92eg_robert-de-niro-and-donald-trump_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frobert-de-niro-says-he-would-never-play-donald-trump-the-guy-is-a-total-monster-5210203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20outspoken%20Oscar-winning%20actor%20said%20he%20would%20not%20want%20Trump%20to%20become%20president%20again%20and%20also%20urged%20voters%20to%20vote%20for%20Joe%20Biden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%