day%20night%20repelled%20gang%20attacks%2C%20including%20on%20the%20presidential%20palace%2C%20and%20several%20%26quot%3Bbandits%26quot%3B%20were%20killed%2C%20Lionel%20Lazarre%20of%20the%20Haitian%20police%20union%20said.%20No%20police%20were%20among%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20left%20burned-out%20vehicles%2C%20still%20smoldering%2C%20outside%20the%20Interior%20Ministry%20and%20on%20nearby%20streets%2C%20an%20AFP%20correspondent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGunshots%20rang%20out%20late%20Friday%20throughout%20Port-au-Prince%20and%20witnesses%20recounted%20clashes%20%26quot%3Bbetween%20police%20officers%20and%20bandits%26quot%3B%20as%20gangs%20apparently%20tried%20to%20commandeer%20police%20stations%20in%20the%20city%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazarre%20on%20Saturday%20pleaded%20for%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20and%20equipment%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20police%20buildings%20and%20other%20key%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20of%20emergency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20well-armed%20gangs%20have%20attacked%20key%20infrastructure%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20including%20two%20prisons%2C%20allowing%20the%20majority%20of%20their%203%2C800%20inmates%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20some%20ordinary%20Haitians%2C%20the%20gangs%20are%20seeking%20the%20resignation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Henry%2C%20who%20was%20due%20to%20leave%20office%20in%20February%20but%20instead%20agreed%20to%20a%20power-sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20opposition%20until%20new%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20asked%20Henry%20to%20enact%20urgent%20political%20reform%20to%20prevent%20further%20escalation.%20But%20he%20was%20in%20Kenya%20when%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20and%20is%20now%20reportedly%20stranded%20in%20the%20US%20territory%20of%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20delays%2C%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20finally%20gave%20its%20green%20light%20in%20October%20for%20a%20multinational%20policing%20mission%20led%20by%20Kenya%2C%20but%20that%20deployment%20has%20been%20stalled%20by%20Kenyan%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPort-au-Prince%20and%20western%20Haiti%20have%20been%20placed%20under%20a%20month-long%20state%20of%20emergency%20and%20a%20nighttime%20curfew%20was%20in%20effect%20until%20Monday%2C%20though%20it%20was%20unlikely%20overstretched%20police%20could%20enforce%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Running%20away'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Port-au-Prince%2C%20Filienne%20Setoute%20told%20AFP%20how%20she%20had%20worked%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Social%20Affairs%20and%20Labor%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20job%2C%20she%20said%2C%20meant%20she%20%26quot%3Bwas%20able%20to%20build%20my%20own%20house.%20But%20now%20here%20I%20am%2C%20homeless.%20I'm%20fleeing%20without%20knowing%20where%20to%20go%2C%20it's%20an%20abuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20sleep%20since%20last%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20running%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaiti's%20airport%20remained%20closed%20while%20the%20main%20port%20--%20a%20key%20point%20for%20food%20imports%20--%20reported%20looting%20since%20suspending%20services%20on%20Thursday%2C%20despite%20efforts%20to%20set%20up%20a%20security%20perimeter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20cannot%20access%20those%20containers%20(full%20of%20food)%2C%20Haiti%20will%20go%20hungry%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NGO%20Mercy%20Corps%20warned%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECARICOM%2C%20an%20alliance%20of%20Caribbean%20nations%2C%20has%20summoned%20envoys%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20France%2C%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20a%20meeting%20Monday%20in%20Jamaica%20to%20discuss%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuyana's%20President%20Irfaan%20Ali%20said%20the%20meeting%20would%20take%20up%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20issues%20for%20the%20stabili