2cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Election%20Commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20Resigned%20Weeks%20Before%202024%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElection%20Commissioner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-facts-on-election-commissioner-arun-goel-who-quit-3-years-before-end-of-his-tenure-5208020%5C%22%3EArun%20Goel%3C%2Fa%3E%20resigned%20on%20Saturday%20just%20days%20before%20the%20anticipated%20announcement%20of%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20officially%20accepted%20Mr%20Goel's%20resignation%2C%20effective%20immediately%2C%20according%20to%20a%20law%20ministry%20notification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Mr%20Goel%20attributed%20his%20resignation%20to%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20reasons%26quot%3B%2C%20despite%20government%20efforts%20to%20dissuade%20him%20from%20stepping%20down.%20Speculation%20regarding%20health%20concerns%20was%20swiftly%20dismissed%2C%20with%20top%20officials%20stating%20that%20Mr%20Goel%20was%20in%20perfect%20health.%20Election%20Commission%20sources%20added%20that%20there%20have%20been%20differences%20on%20file%20between%20Mr%20Goel%20and%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20consisting%20of%20three%20members%2C%20already%20had%20a%20vacant%20position%2C%20and%20now%2C%20only%20Mr%20Kumar%20remains%20on%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20bureaucrat%2C%20Mr%20Goel%2C%20a%201985-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Punjab%20cadre%2C%20joined%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20dates%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20next%20week.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Goel's%20unexpected%20departure%20has%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20previously%20anticipated%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happens%20Next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20process%20for%20a%20new%20CEC%20involves%20a%20search%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20the%20law%20minister%20and%20including%20two%20union%20secretaries%2C%20shortlisting%20five%20names.%20Subsequently%2C%20a%20selection%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20comprising%20a%20Union%20Cabinet%20Minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20PM%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20or%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20single-largest%20opposition%20party%2C%20selects%20the%20final%20candidate.%20The%20President%20then%20formally%20appoints%20the%20chosen%20CEC%20or%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20move%20that%20preceded%20Mr%20Goel's%20resignation%20was%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20new%20law%20late%20last%20year%2C%20altering%20the%20process%20of%20appointing%20the%20country's%20top%20election%20officers.%20Under%20the%20revised%20procedure%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20was%20excluded%20from%20the%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Said%20What%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20question%20the%20implications%20of%20Mr%20Goel's%20sudden%20departure.%20He%20asked%20whether%20the%20current%20state%20of%20affairs%20warranted%20renaming%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20%26quot%3BElection%20OMISSION%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElection%20Commission%20or%20Election%20OMISSION%3F%20India%20now%20has%20only%20one%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20even%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20to%20be%20announced%20in%20few%20days.%20Why%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20I%20have%20said%20earlier%2C%20if%20we%20do%20not%20stop%20the%20systematic%20decimation%20of%20our%20independent%20institutions%2C%20our%20democracy%20shall%20be%20usurped%20by%20dictatorship!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20new%20process%20of%20selecting%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%20have%20now%20effectively%20given%20all%20the%20power%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20PM%2C%20why%20has%20the%20new%20Election%20Commissioner%20not%20appointed%20even%20after%2023%20days%20of%20the%20completion%20of%20latter's%20tenure%3F%20Modi%20government%20must%20answer%20these%20questions%20and%20come%20out%20with%20a%20reasonable%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20or%20Election%20OMISSION%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20now%20has%20only%20ONE%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20even%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20to%20be%20announced%20in%20few%20days.%20Why%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20I%20have%20said%20earlier%2C%20if%20we%20do%20NOT%20stop%20the%20systematic%20decimation%20of%20our%20independent%20institutions%2C%20our%20DEMOCRACY%20shall%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1766514087188435427%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20organisation%20KC%20Venugopal%20echoed%20Mr%20Kharge's%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20deeply%20concerning%20for%20the%20health%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%20that%20Election%20Commissioner%20Mr%20Arun%20Goel%20has%20resigned%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20expressed%20worry%20about%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20government%20on%20constitutional%20bodies%2C%20citing%20the%20example%20of%20Ashok%20Lavasa's%20dissent%20during%20the%202019%20elections%20and%20subsequent%20inquiries.%20Mr%20Lavasa%20had%20resigned%20citin