%20Environment%2C%20Forests%20and%20Climate%20Change%20(MoEFCC)%20to%20revert%20to%20the%20previous%2C%20more%20comprehensive%20definition%20of%20forests.%20This%20broader%20definition%20aligns%20with%20the%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleap.unep.org%2Fen%2Fcountries%2Fin%2Fnational-case-law%2Ftn-godavarman-thirumulpad-versus-union-india%5C%22%3E1996%20Godavarman%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20limited%20definition%20found%20in%20the%20recently%20amended%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202015%20to%20March%202020%2C%20the%20government%20approved%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fenvironment-vs-economy-indias-flawed-logic-that-exposes-it-to-covid-19-like-infections%2F%5C%22%3Econversion%20of%20409%20sq.km%20of%20forest%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20various%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMega%20projects%2C%20mega%20messes%3A%20Environmental%20and%20social%20impacts%20of%20large-scale%20projects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20its%20penchant%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fslogans-acronyms-and-self-congratulation-2877799%5C%22%3Eself-praise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NDA%20government%20will%20beat%20the%20trumpet%20on%20the%20increased%20government%20investments%20on%20infrastructure.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%20infrastructure%20has%20surged%20notably%20from%20FY%202018-19%20to%20FY%202024-25%2C%20witnessing%20a%20remarkable%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cenfa.org%2Fincreasing-pace-of-infra-dvpt-in-india%2F%5C%22%3E%20269.82%25%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20capital%20expenditure%20allocation.%20As%20per%20the%20records%20of%20Land%20Conflict%20Watch%2C%20more%20than%204.6%20million%20individuals%20have%20been%20impacted%20by%20land-related%20disputes%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landconflictwatch.org%2Fall-conflicts%5C%22%3Einf