insider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-future-will-not-be-free-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20further%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadopted%2C%20it%20could%20drain%20significantly%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20Google%20integrated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-reliant-on-big-tech-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20every%20search%2C%20it%20would%20drain%20about%2029%20billion%20kilowatt-hours%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20calculations%20made%20by%20Alex%20de%20Vries%2C%20a%20data%20scientist%20for%20the%20Dutch%20National%20Bank%2C%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fjoule%2Fabstract%2FS2542-4351(23)00365-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20sustainable%20energy%20journal%20Joule.%20That's%20more%20electricity%20than%20countries%20like%20Kenya%2C%20Guatemala%2C%20and%20Croatia%20consume%20in%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20Yorker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20just%20very%20energy%20intensive%2C%26quot%3B%20de%20Vries%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-industry-energy-study-small-country-enviroment-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20of%20these%20AI%20servers%20can%20already%20consume%20as%20much%20power%20as%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20UK%20households%20combined.%20So%20the%20numbers%20add%20up%20really%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20estimating%20how%20much%20electricity%20the%20booming%20AI%20industry%20consumes%20is%20tough%20to%20pin%20down.%20There's%20considerable%20variability%20in%20how%20large%20AI%20models%20operate%2C%20and%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20which%20have%20been%20driving%20the%20boom%20%E2%80%94%20haven't%20been%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexactly%20forthcoming%20about%20their%20ene