ages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEpic%20Games%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20have%20its%20own%20app%20store%20on%20IOS%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20reversed%20its%20decision%20not%20to%20allow%20the%20Epic%20Games%20Store%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEpic%2C%20which%20makes%20Fortnite%2C%20has%20been%20battling%20Apple%20and%20Google%20over%20in-app%20purchases%20for%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20backing%20down%20after%20saying%20it%20would%20not%20allow%20Epic%20Games%20to%20have%20its%20own%20app%20store%20on%20IOS%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20decided%20to%20reverse%20its%20decision%20following%20a%20claim%20by%20European%20Union%20officials%20that%20they%20would%20investigate%20the%20ban%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F08%2Ftech%2Fapple-fortnite-epic-games-eu-investigation%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20Games%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-fortnite-epic-games-lawsuit-secrets-revealed-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20makes%20Fortnite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20been%20battling%20Google%20and%20Apple%20to%20get%20around%20their%20hold%20on%20in-app%20purchases%20on%20their%20platforms%20in%20recent%20years.%20Both%20Google%20and%20Apple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffortnite-removed-from-app-store-how-to-download-iphone-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoved%20Fortnite%20from%20their%20online%20stores%20in%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Epic%20created%20a%20way%20to%20purchase%20in-game%20currency%20that%20didn't%20use%20the%20in-app%20purchasing%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epicgames.com%2Fsite%2Fen-US%2Fnews%2Fapple-terminated-epic-s-developer-account%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%