3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20and%20copilot%20of%20a%20domestic%20flight%20in%20Indonesia%20carrying%20153%20people%20fell%20asleep%20for%20nearly%2030%20minutes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fknkt.go.id%2FRepo%2FFiles%2FLaporan%2FPenerbangan%2F2024%2FKNKT.24.01.02.04-Preliminary-Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20published%20by%20Indonesia's%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Committee%20(KNKT)%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20in%20January%20on%20a%20return%20flight%20from%20Kendari%2C%20in%20the%20Indonesian%20province%20of%20Southeast%20Sulawesi%2C%20to%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20of%20the%20Batik%20Air%20%3Cspan%3EAirbus%20%3C%2Fspan%3EA320%20aircraft%2C%2032%2C%20took%20a%20nap%20after%20getting%20permission%20from%20his%20copilot%20while%20the%20plane%20was%20at%20a%20cruising%20altitude%20of%2036%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2045%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20captain%20woke%20up%20and%20offered%20to%20let%20the%20copilot%2C%2028%2C%20rest%2C%20but%20they%20declined%2C%20and%20the%20captain%20fell%20back%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20officer%20spent%20roughly%20the%20next%2020%20minutes%20communicating%20with%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20and%20flight%20attendants%20before%20they%20%26quot%3Binadvertently%26quot%3B%20also%20fell%20asleep%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20minutes%20after%20the%20copilot's%20last%20recorded%20transmission%2C%20the%20captain%20woke%20up%20and%20saw%20that%20his%20second%20in%20command%20was%20asleep%20and%20that%20they%20had%20flown%20off-course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20waking%20them%2C%20the%20captain%20answered%20another%20pilot's%20call%20and%20air%20traffic%20controllers%2C%20claiming%20they%20had%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bradio%20communication%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20later%20landed%20in%20Jakarta%20without%20any%20further%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20long-haul%20flights%20have%20relief%20pilots%20to%20ensure%20each%20pilot%20is%20sufficiently%20rested%20when%20they%20take%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20short-haul%20flights%20such%20as%20the%20Batik%20Air%20flight%2C%20which%20takes%20roughly%20two%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflightsafety.org%2Fasw-article%2Fcontrolled-rest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtrolled%20rest%20periods%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20more%20common%3A%20One%20pilot%20can%20briefly%20catch%20some%20shut-eye%20while%20the%20other%20continues%20monitoring%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20manage%20fatigue%20and%20improve%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20KNKT%20report%2C%20the%20second%20in%20command%20had%20not%20rested%20sufficiently%20the%20night%20before%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20pilots'%20identities%20but%20said%20both%20were%20Indonesian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20acknowledged%20%26quot%3Bthe%20safety%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20aircraft%20operator%20and%20considered%20that%20the%20safety%20actions%20were%20relevant%20to%20improve%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20did%20make%20some%20safety%20recommendations%20over%20adding%20guidance%20on%20checking%20pilots'%20physical%20and%20mental%20conditions%20and%20carrying%20out%20cockpit%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatik%20Air%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Boperates%20with%20adequate%20rest%20policy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20implement%20all%20safety%20recommendation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-13176837%2FPilot-pilot-fall-ASLEEP-28-minutes-passenger-flight-Indonesia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMailOnline%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Batik%20Air%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710009431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eca6dfce7f1785b2e8430e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20occurred%20on%20a%20Batik%20Air%20return%20flight%20carrying%20153%20people%20to%20the%20Indonesian%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmanley%40businessinsider.com%20(Cameron%20Manley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2-pilots-batik-air-a320-fall-asleep-28-minutes-report-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dating%20apps%20confused%20by%20military%20GPS%20jamming%20could%20explain%20why%20Lebanon's%20citizens%20are%20suddenly%20being%20matched%20with%20Israelis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20taken%20from%20northern%20Israel%2C%20along%20the%20border%20with%20southern%20Lebanon%20on%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20shows%20smoke%20billowing%20following%20Israeli%20bombardment%20on%20the%20Lebanese%20village%20of%20Markaba.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ec7c9090413ab8e1db2bdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221386%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20picture%20taken%20from%20northern%20Israel%2C%20along%20the%20border%20with%20southern%20Lebanon%20on%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20shows%20smoke%20billowing%20following%20Israeli%20bombardment%20on%20the%20Lebanese%20village%20of%20Markaba.%3Cp%3EJalaa%20Marey%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDating%20apps%20matching%20Israeli%20citizens%20with%20people%20in%20Lebanon%20are%20likely%20due%20to%20GPS%20signal%20jamming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20confusion%20comes%20amid%20heightened%20tensions%20and%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELebanese%20citizens%20are%20barred%20from%20having%20any%20type%20of%20contact%20with%20Israelis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20apps%20confused%20by%20GPS%20signal%20jamming%20are%20being%20blamed%20for%20matching%20Israeli%20citizens%20with%20people%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20its%20neighboring%20country%20that%20it%20is%20currently%20in%20conflict%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalnews.com%2Fmena%2F2024%2F03%2F05%2Fisraeli-gps-interference-disrupting-lebanese-location-services-and-dating-apps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpress%20confusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20their%20dating%20app%20feeds%20are%20now%20filled%20with%20people%20from%20the%20other%20country%2C%20the%20UAE-owned%20newspaper%20The%20National%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel%2C%20tensions%20escalated%20in%20the%20region%2C%20with%20the%20Lebanese%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20and%20the%20Israeli%20army%20conducting%20strikes%20with%20drones%2C%20missiles%2C%20and%20artillery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20were%20high%20between%20the%20countries%20even%20before%20the%20latest%20conflict%2C%20and%20Lebanese%20citizens%20have%20been%20barred%20from%20having%20any%20contact%20with%20Israelis%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20Lebanese%20dating%20app%20user%20said%20the%20Israeli%20profiles%20were%20'gorgeous'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tinder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5acf9d7ffacba819008b4637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20match%20is%20not%20always%20what%20it%20seems.%3Cp%3EMr.%20Whiskey%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20explained%20that%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20dating%20app%20confusion%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fisraels-using-widespread-gps-tampering-to-deter-hezbollahs-missiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Israel's%20military%20use%20of%20GPS%20jamming%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prevent%20attacks%20coming%20from%20Lebanon%2C%20which%20might%20confuse%20phones%20into%20thinking%20the%20users%20are%20located%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20affecting%20not%20only%20dating%20apps%20but%20also%20different%20applications%20that%20have%20access%20to%20GPS%20to%20identify%20the%20user's%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20Abed%20Al%20Kataya%2C%20a%20media%20program%20manager%20at%20a%20digital%20rights%20organization%20in%20Beirut%2C%20told%20The%20National.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterfering%20with%20GPS%20also%20endangers%20civilian%20and%20commercial%20maritime%20and%20aerial%20traffic%2C%20potentially%20causing%20navigation%20failures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20profiles%20accounted%20for%2060-62%25%20of%20the%20total%20on%20Tinder%20in%20Lebanon%20in%20February%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Lebanese%20newspaper%20L'Orient-Le%20Jour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20war%20started%2C%20I%20mostly%20see%20Israelis%20on%20the%20app%20%E2%80%94%20I%20barely%20use%20it%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Beirut%20resident%20Maher%2C%20per%20The%20National.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Israel%20are%20reporting%20a%20similar%20problem%2C%20with%20a%20reservist%20soldier%20taking%20to%20Facebook%20to%20express%20confusion%20that%20many%20of%20his%20recent%20dating%20app%20matches%20are%20based%20in%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20joked%20that%20if%20Israel%20decided%20to%20go%20after%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20he%20hoped%20he%20would%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20his%20new%20matches%2C%20according%20to%20The%20National.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20in%20the%20reserves%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20the%20army%20decides%20to%20get%20that%20maniac%20in%20the%20north%2C%20I%20request%20that%20my%20country%20calls%20me%20to%20arms%20once%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Lebanese%20dating%20app%20user%2C%20Omar%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20previously%20seen%20the%20occasional%20Israeli%20profile%2C%20the%20volume%20has%20recently%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20The%20National%2C%20he%20said%20about%20the%20Israeli%20profiles%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20keep%20seeing%20them%2C%20and%20they're%20absolutely%20gorgeous%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20do%20anything%20because%20we're%20divided%20by%20an%20apartheid%20wall%20and%20a%20genocidal%20army%20that%20doesn't%20take%20too%20well%20to%20Arabs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-israelis-and-lebanese-are-suddenly-getting-dating-app-matches-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710009060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ec7d3090413ab8e1db2bec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-israelis-and-lebanese-are-suddenly-getting-dating-app-matches-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dating%20apps%20in%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20are%20matching%20users%20from%20the%20nations%2C%20despite%20a%20ban%20on%20contact.%20GPS%20signal%20jamming%20could%20be%20to%20blame.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-israelis-and-lebanese-are-suddenly-getting-dating-app-matches-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ibrahim-Palak%20step%20out%20in%20the%20city%20together%3A%20PICS%2