%2F09211120%2FFotoJet-7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20on%20Saturday%20(March%209)%20announced%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20three%20parties%20said%20that%20their%20coming%20together%20with%20the%20two%20parties%20will%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20in%20reaching%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20and%20TDP%20have%20a%20very%20old%20relationship%20together.%20TDP%20joined%20NDA%20in%201996%20and%20has%20worked%20together%20successfully%20in%20Atal%20Ji%E2%80%99s%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%C2%A0%20Ji%E2%80%99%20government.%20In%C2%A0%202014%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%C2%A0%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20assembly%20election%20together.%20The%C2%A0%20JSP%C2%A0%20had%20supported%20the%202014%C2%A0%20general%20and%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20alliance%20has%20been%20sealed%2C%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20formally%20announced.%20The%20BJP%20said%20that%20the%20modalities%20will%20be%20deliberated%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20alliance%20was%20sealed%2C%20Naidu%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20sweep%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAndhra%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20destroyed%20badly.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20TDP%20coming%20together%20is%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20second%20round%20of%20talks%20between%2