in%20all%20its%20glory%20and%20is%20certain%20to%20leave%20you%20breathless%2C%20as%20it%20did%20for%20Samit%20Sawhny%20(52)%20when%20he%20first%20set%20foot%20on%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20coast.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202001%2C%20I%20took%20a%20few%20years%E2%80%99s%20break%20from%20work%20to%20travel%20the%20world.%20When%20I%20reached%20Havelock%2C%20it%20took%20my%20breath%20away%2C%20and%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20leave%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoaming%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20island%2C%20he%20realised%20his%20desire%20to%20contribute%20to%20its%20allure.%20The%20result%3F%20%E2%80%98Barefoot%20at%20Havelock.%E2%80%99%20True%20to%20its%20name%2C%20the%20resort%20offers%20a%20chance%20for%20visitors%20to%20fully%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20eco-friendly%20cottages%20nestled%20amidst%20lush%20tropical%20foliage%20to%20luxurious%20beachfront%20villas%20boasting%20panoramic%20views%20of%20the%20azure%20sea%2C%20the%20resort%20caters%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20tastes%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20tipping%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20life%20before%20he%20founded%20Barefoot%2C%20Samit%20reflects%20on%20his%20initial%20career%20aspirations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20path%20in%20finance%20and%20meticulously%20selected%20prestigious%20colleges%20to%20lead%20me%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Chennai%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342428%2Fgujarat-daman-thakore-family-drives-vintage-car-from-ahmedabad-to-london-europe-road-trip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20relocated%20to%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20upon%20completing%20his%20graduation%20and%20commenced%20employment%20at%20a%20renowned%20firm.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20of%20working%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20corporate%20finance%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20me.%20It%20lacked%20the%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20I%20sought.%20Despite%20the%20arduous%20journey%20to%20secure%20such%20a%20position%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20academic%20challenges%2C%20seeking%20out%20the%20right%20institutions%2C%20and%20cultivating%20the%20necessary%20connections%2C%20the%20work%20became%20somewhat%20mundane.%20While%20the%20field%20suits%20many%2C%20I%20yearned%20for%20something%20more%20tangible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20then%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20India.%20%E2%80%9CUpon%20my%20return%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20at%20a%20crossroads%20with%20no%20clear%20direction.%20It%20felt%20like%20starting%20anew.%20I%20opted%20to%20take%20some%20time%20off%20and%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Fbw7USCmL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Fbw7USCmL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Fbw7USCmL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Barefoot%20in%20the%20Andamans%20(%40barefootintheandamans)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20seven-month%20expedition%2C%20he%20serendipitously%20found%20himself%20in%20Havelock%2C%20captivated%20by%20its%20breathtaking%20beauty.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20struck%20me%20was%20the%20sheer%20lack%20of%20tourism%20in%20this%20stunning%20locale.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20hidden%20paradise%2C%20secluded%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20Recognising%20its%20potential%2C%20especially%20for%20nature%20lovers%20seeking%20a%20tranquil%20escape%2C%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20start%20an%20eco-friendly%20venture%20on%20the%20island%2C%20without%20disturbing%20its%20natural%20beauty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20property%20blends%20into%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20isolation%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20was%20its%20appeal%2C%20Sumit%20realised%20this%20USP%20also%20came%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20major%20issue%20that%20I%20could%20see%20was%20that%20since%20I%20was%20the%20first%20one%20to%20start%20something%20like%20this%20on%20the%20island%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20connectivity.%20There%20were%20no%20regular%20ferries%2C%20and%20the%20available%20ones%20were%20painfully%20slow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20place%20was%20very%20poor%2C%20and%20before%20Samit%20could%20begin%20work%20on%20his%20resort%2C%20he%20had%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20making%20it%20accessible%20to%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20was%20an%20important%20lesson%20learned%20from%20this%20experience.%20Havelock%20was%20Havelock%20for%20this%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20fewer%20crowds%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335433%2Fnorthstar-school-rajkot-sustainable-design-santiniketan-open-learning-ib-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20nature.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20place%20is%20not%20like%20the%20Maldives%20or%20any%20other%20tourist%20destination.%20People%20come%20here%20for%20a%20truly%20natural%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20concluded%20that%20opening%20a%20resort%20even%20deeper%20into%20the%20island%20would%20not%20be%20wise%20due%20to%20the%20connectivity%20issue.%20Therefore%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20build%20the%20property%20alongside%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20come%20to%20the%20island%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20combination%20of%20thick%20woods%20and%20beaches.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20resort%20that%20blends%20into%20the%20natural%20surroundings%20and%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20wildlife%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samit%20Founder%20of%20Barefoot%20at%20Havelock%20Sawhny.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-17-1709819752-150x79.jpg%