0daughter-in-law%2C%20helping%20them%20gain%20financial%20freedom%20and%20giving%20wings%20to%20their%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20an%20age%20old%20problem%20faced%20by%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20make%20the%20hair%20oil%20using%2013%20ingredients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343983%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20make%20the%20hair%20oil%20using%2013%20ingredients%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENidhi%20had%20a%20thriving%20career%20as%20a%20software%20engineer.%20Her%20priorities%20shifted%20after%20she%20was%20alerted%20about%20some%20behavioural%20issues%20in%20her%20son%20(then%203)%20in%202016.%20She%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20focus%20on%20him.%20While%20she%20missed%20her%20job%2C%20she%20found%20that%20her%20son%20needed%20her%20the%20most%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20toyed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoining%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20at%20some%20time%2C%20but%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20hair%20oil%20in%202020%20pleasantly%20surprised%20her.%20It%20took%20her%20back%20to%20her%20conversations%20with%20her%20grandmother%2C%20when%20she%20would%20ask%20her%20why%20she%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20making%20this%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Edaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20would%20sit%20with%20this%20iron%20%3Cem%3Ekadhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(large%20vessel)%20every%20week%2C%20and%20spend%20hours%20stirring%20the%20oil%2C%20adding%2013%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20She%20used%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20I%20would%20realise%20its%20worth%20after%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nidhi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20just%20as%20the%20wise%20woman%20had%20predicted%2C%20Nidhi%20turned%20to%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20when%20she%20faced%20the%20massive%20challenge%20of%20hairfall.%20The%20duo%20made%20the%20oil%20together%2C%20which%20took%20an%20entire%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20tremendous%20hair%20fall.%20After%20using%20it%20for%20about%20two-three%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20our%20hairfall%20had%20greatly%20reduced%20and%20our%20hair%20was%20growing.%20I%20started%20making%20it%20for%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20domestic%20help%2C%20who%20also%20found%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20